                     <interp inst="t18290115-110-person871" type="gender" value="female"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I am the prosecutor's daughter. I saw the prisoner take it off the box, and put it over his shoulder - I have not the least doubt of his person.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18290115-110-person872">
                  JOHN 
                  COX
